<h5><strong>5. Will editors and reviewers see this checklist?
</strong></h5>
<p>
    <strong>Yes</strong>, the checklist will be available for editors and reviewers
</p>
<h5><strong>6. Will this checklist be published with the manuscript?
</strong></h5>
<p>
